⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Penthouse</xex> lid.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Shak.</au> ⟦ldquo⟧My
<xex>penthouse</xex> eyebrows.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Dryden.</au>⟦br⟧
